<view class="page">
  <view class="page__hd">
    <view class="page__title">关于绑定</view>
    <view class="weui-article">
      <view class="weui-article__section">
        <view class="weui-article__p">
          如果你已经有了玻璃渣游戏安全令在线版的账号，请绑定账号到微信小程序，即可直接读取账号中的安全令数据，小程序中的所有操作均直接同步到线上。
        </view>
      </view>
    </view>
  </view>
  <form bindsubmit="formSubmit" bindreset="formReset">
    <view class="weui-cell">
      <view class="weui-cell__hd">
        <label class="weui-label">账号</label>
      </view>
      <view class="weui-cell__bd">
        <input class="weui-input" type="text" pattern="[0-9]*" placeholder="请输入需要绑定的账号" name="username" confirm-type='done' />
      </view>
    </view>
    <view class="weui-cell">
      <view class="weui-cell__hd">
        <label class="weui-label">密码</label>
      </view>
      <view class="weui-cell__bd">
        <input class="weui-input" type="password" pattern="[0-9]*" placeholder="输入密码" name='password' confirm-type='done' />
      </view>
    </view>
    <view class="btn-area">
      <button type="primary" size="{{defaultSize}}" loading="{{loading}}" plain="{{plain}}" disabled="{{disabled}}" bindtap="click" form-type="submit" id="bind1">点击绑定</button>
    </view>

    <view class="btn-area">
      <button type='warn' bindtap="register">注册新账号</button>
    </view>
  </form>
</view>